Package ua.training.model.knight

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAmmunitionCarrier
    Interface describes behaviour of some entity, which can operate with ChainArmor, Helmet, Shield, Weapon objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractKnightBuilder
    This class provides a skeletal implementation of the Knight interface to minimize the effort required to implement this interface.
    Knight
    Implementation of IAmmunitionCarrier interface, which presents knight.
    KnightBuilder
    Implementation of AbstractKnightBuilder abstract class.
